lead_paragraph: Courtney Walker scored 29 points, including 10 in overtime, and No. 12 Texas A&M bounced back from two straight losses to beat No. 23 Tennessee 76-71 on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: No. 12 Texas A&M Women Beat No. 23 Tennessee 76-71 in OT
